RACE.FOOTNOTES: CHOSEN JUDGE (IRE) went unhurried early, ridden forward to challenge leader on the final turn, dueled and prevailed driving. TRAVESURAS settled in the rear, moved up on the final turn, drew even with CHOSEN JUDGE and battled with that one to the wire, finishing second a length back. HOLD HARD (IRE) traveled mid pack, always close up, finishing evenly one paced. FLOP SHOT (IRE) was rated, ridden forward on the final turn, then weakened in the stretch. JUST ANOTHER ONE (IRE) was no threat and outrun late. REASSURED traveled close up till the final furn, then tired and was pulled up. BEOWULF (IRE) showed speed for one circuit, then tired and was pulled up. CASAMO trailed and was pulled up. FINDING FREEDOM set the pace for the first circuit, then tired and was pulled up. IN EFFECT lost rider over a hurdle towards the completion of the first circuit.

RACE.FOOTNOTES: ROCKET ONE rated well, closed strongly exiting the final turn, got a narrow lead over the last hurdle and prevailed driving.
